      "uco-core:description": "T Document 144 Filed 10/29/24 Page 5 of 20\n\nPROCEDURAL BACKGROUND\n\nTeixeira was arrested by the Federal Bureau of Investigation on April 13, 2023, and, the\n\nnext day, was charged by complaint with violating 1",
      "uco-core:eventContext": [
